WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.990
Hey, good morning family. I just want to

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.949
say thank you to all the people who

00:00:03.959 --> 00:00:06.309
came out for the Arise Conference

00:00:06.319 --> 00:00:09.310
with Sister Billie and Rick Renner. It was

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:11.470
wonderful. We have one more

00:00:11.480 --> 00:00:14.270
day, which is Sunday, and we're having

00:00:14.280 --> 00:00:16.349
services tomorrow morning

00:00:16.349 --> 00:00:16.359
and

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:18.790
tomorrow night at 7:00. We're

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:20.269
excited about it;

00:00:20.269 --> 00:00:20.279
it’s

00:00:20.279 --> 00:00:22.429
the finale, and I'm believing God

00:00:22.439 --> 00:00:24.870
for a major move of His presence, a

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:28.750
glorious outpouring of His Spirit on the

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:30.990
last night, which is tomorrow night.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.270
It's been so exciting to

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:35.110
see every single one of you. Thank you

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:38.110
for driving so far to be a part of this

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:39.630
conference. There were a lot of you

00:00:39.630 --> 00:00:39.640
who

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:41.869
drove from all over the place, from Maine

00:00:41.879 --> 00:00:44.830
to Michigan. I talked to

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.670
a man from Colorado who

00:00:47.670 --> 00:00:47.680
has

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:49.189
been coming to all the

00:00:49.199 --> 00:00:51.470
meetings, so it's exciting to see your

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:54.709
faces.

00:00:54.709 --> 00:00:54.719
It’s

00:00:54.719 --> 00:00:56.910
great to

00:01:00.910 --> 00:01:00.920
put

00:01:02.879 --> 00:01:05.310
a face with the name

00:01:05.310 --> 00:01:05.320
from

00:01:05.320 --> 00:01:07.390
an email and say, 'Oh, that's

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:09.870
who you are.'It’s exciting because

00:01:09.870 --> 00:01:09.880
y’all

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.390
are so kind; you

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:15.030
email us and always try to encourage us,

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:18.270
and you're so faithful.

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:20.109
I think it's interesting, I have some

00:01:20.119 --> 00:01:23.789
things on my heart. Bill Gates

00:01:23.799 --> 00:01:26.190
went on *The View*. Some people sent this

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.830
to me and said, 'Brandon, did you see

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.030
what Bill Gates said on *The View* about the

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:33.469
plague and all that?'I said,

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:36.389
'Go

00:01:36.389 --> 00:01:36.399
figure,'but

00:01:36.399 --> 00:01:39.710
he went on *The View* and

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:41.069
told everybody that he thought there

00:01:41.079 --> 00:01:42.630
would be another plague happening within

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:46.109
the next four years—a major one, worse

00:01:46.119 --> 00:01:48.789
than COVID—just like I told you all that

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:50.789
they were planning something worse than

00:01:50.789 --> 00:01:50.799
COVID,

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:53.429
like the Black Death.

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:55.230
He went on to say all these dark

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.709
things. Let me show you that little

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:58.830
clip right here.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:01.310
Before COVID, you said you spent the most

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:03.789
sleepless nights worrying about

00:02:03.799 --> 00:02:07.469
pandemics. After COVID, has that changed?

00:02:07.479 --> 00:02:09.990
And if it has, what keeps you up now?

00:02:09.990 --> 00:02:10.000
Because

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.270
we all need to

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:16.710
know. Yeah, the pandemic, sadly, was

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.309
fairly predictable, and it won't be

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:21.910
the last pandemic. The next one could

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:25.030
be far more severe. I mean, this one

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:28.390
killed millions; it was awful. We got

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:30.869
the vaccine.

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:33.589
President Trump's leadership was a

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:35.830
factor in getting that out quickly.

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.150
When I spoke to him, I said, 'Here

00:02:38.150 --> 00:02:38.160
are

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.229
some other medical innovations,

00:02:40.239 --> 00:02:42.070
including a thing called an HIV cure

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:44.390
that could be

00:02:44.390 --> 00:02:44.400
accelerated.'So,

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:48.270
we should be more

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:50.790
prepared for a pandemic; I'd say

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:53.589
that's still number one. You

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:56.309
can worry about nuclear war, AI—oh, there’s

00:02:56.309 --> 00:02:56.319
plenty to

00:02:56.319 --> 00:03:01.589
worry

00:03:01.589 --> 00:03:01.599
about—but

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:04.830
overall, I'm an

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:07.750
optimist. It’s up to

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:09.630
the government to think ahead on behalf

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:12.949
of the citizens. Regarding a pandemic,

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:15.589
there's a lot that we should be doing

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:17.990
that hopefully we'll get our act

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:20.030
together before the next one comes.

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:23.309
Overall, innovation in health, both

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:25.110
in developing countries and the rich

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:27.509
world, I love being part of

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:29.229
that. I was reading, though, that you said

00:03:29.239 --> 00:03:31.830
the next pandemic you are predicting within

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:33.750
maybe 25 years. Is that certain? Certainly, we'll

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:38.030
have one in the next 25 years. There

00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:38.040
are

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:40.110
even some pathogens out

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:43.390
there that we're watching right now.

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:46.550
So, maybe a 10% chance in the

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:49.229
next four years. Folks, they're

00:03:49.239 --> 00:03:51.470
telling you what they're planning; it's

00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:53.830
how they're going to try to derail

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:56.869
Trump's presidency to try to not let

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:58.190
him do all the things he’s wanting

00:03:58.200 --> 00:04:01.910
to do. I saw the darkness of them

00:04:01.910 --> 00:04:01.920
trying—the

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:05.229
Antichrist agenda trying to stop

00:04:05.239 --> 00:04:07.429
and derail the things that God was

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:11.910
trying to do. Now, I believe the plague

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:14.390
has a great opportunity to take

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:17.310
place; maybe we can delay it, maybe we

00:04:17.320 --> 00:04:19.990
can't, but I'm telling you all it's not

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:23.870
for us to fear. The Lord said if you get

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:26.909
Psalm

00:04:26.919 --> 00:04:30.550
91 deep down inside of your

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:33.909
heart and Psalm 23—I told you all I saw

00:04:33.919 --> 00:04:37.189
a major storm coming on the East Coast; a

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:40.790
major storm was coming and it starts in

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:43.870
Europe. The Lord showed me a great

00:04:43.880 --> 00:04:47.350
shaking to awaken is coming.

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:49.830
Whenever I

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:52.710
talked to Sister Billie, she said, 'Brandon,

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:55.070
we want something greater than a

00:04:55.070 --> 00:04:55.080
revival,'and

00:04:55.080 --> 00:04:57.350
what's greater than a

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.990
revival is an awakening unto God.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:00.990
That's what the Lord told me:

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.830
'Brandon, I'm going to bring an awakening

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:05.510
to the church. There's a great shaking to

00:05:05.510 --> 00:05:05.520
awaken.'So,

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:07.950
I want you all to be

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.909
encouraged that this isn't about fear

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:10.749
for

00:05:10.759 --> 00:05:15.749
you

00:05:15.749 --> 00:05:15.759
Bible-believing,

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:20.469
Holy Ghost-filled,

00:05:20.469 --> 00:05:20.479
on-fire-for-Jesus

00:05:20.479 --> 00:05:24.430
people. This is a time to arise

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:26.350
and shine for the light has come and the

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:28.950
glory of the Lord is risen upon you. This

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:31.230
is not going to be a time for you to go,

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:34.350
'Oh no, Chicken Little, the sky is

00:05:34.350 --> 00:05:34.360
falling.'I

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:37.189
do not believe that. I believe it's

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:39.990
time for the glorious church to rise up

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:42.870
and take their authority like we've

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:45.270
never seen before. The

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.749
Bible says that He's coming for a bride

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:49.350
without spot or

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:52.510
wrinkle, and we will be that glorious

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:55.150
church. What is it going to take to

00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:59.749
get there? I was standing

00:05:59.749 --> 00:05:59.759
there

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:03.110
getting my daughter ready for church

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:05.790
tonight and the Lord spoke to me.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.230
I was frustrated because I was

00:06:07.240 --> 00:06:08.390
brushing her hair and

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:10.189
helping Diana get ready because

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:12.510
we were running late, and the Lord spoke

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.110
to me. He said,

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:16.909
'Brandon, when are you

00:06:16.919 --> 00:06:19.870
going to shift your thinking for Megan

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:22.749
to believe for her

00:06:22.749 --> 00:06:22.759
now?'She's

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:26.430
healed instead of

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:26.440
always—because

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:27.629
He heard my

00:06:27.629 --> 00:06:27.639
heart—complaining

00:06:27.639 --> 00:06:29.710
about what I was doing.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:31.990
He said to me, 'When are you going to

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:34.790
believe Me that today is the

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:37.589
day? Why is it that your heart is

00:06:37.599 --> 00:06:39.670
always, "Well,

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:42.710
it'll come one day; her

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.629
manifestation is going to come one

00:06:44.629 --> 00:06:44.639
day"?'I

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:46.749
believe it. He said, 'When are you going

00:06:46.759 --> 00:06:48.710
to shift it to now-faith as the substance

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:50.230
of things hoped for and evidence of things

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.629
not

00:06:51.639 --> 00:06:54.110
seen? When are you going to believe for

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:58.110
her now,

00:06:58.120 --> 00:07:00.350
Brandon? Why not?'And then He said this to

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:03.469
me: 'Why not

00:07:03.479 --> 00:07:05.990
tonight? Why not

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.230
tonight? And if not

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:10.950
tonight, why not tomorrow

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:13.670
night? Why do you put off in your mind

00:07:13.670 --> 00:07:13.680
that

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.830
this may happen in a couple of

00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:15.840
years?'That's

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:17.909
what He was correcting me on. I

00:07:17.919 --> 00:07:20.629
stopped and said, 'Lord...'He said, 'When are

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:22.550
you believing for it? When do you really

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:25.830
believe for it? Why are you believing for

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:29.830
years from now? Believe Me for the

00:07:29.830 --> 00:07:29.840
now.'So

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:32.390
I want to encourage you all: there's a

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:35.469
lot of things you've been believing

00:07:35.479 --> 00:07:39.029
for, like finances, and it may not seem like

00:07:39.039 --> 00:07:41.830
you're ever going to get out of poverty,

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:47.070
get a good job, or

00:07:47.070 --> 00:07:47.080
that

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:48.670
your marriage is ever going to turn

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:53.110
around, but suddenly things change.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.869
Joseph was in

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:58.589
prison

00:07:58.589 --> 00:07:58.599
for

00:07:58.599 --> 00:08:00.670
14

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:03.550
years, but he didn't know

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:05.589
all his circumstances were going to

00:08:05.599 --> 00:08:07.749
change in a 24-hour period and he was

00:08:07.759 --> 00:08:10.469
going to be second-in-command of all

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:14.070
Egypt. There was a 'suddenly.'There is a

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:16.589
time where all the trials and the things

00:08:16.599 --> 00:08:18.230
you've been going through will have an

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:21.550
expiration date. When is your expiration

00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:23.189
date? The Lord said for your life and

00:08:23.199 --> 00:08:26.309
what you're believing for, when is that

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:29.110
time of that miracle coming

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:31.830
for you? If we're always believing

00:08:31.830 --> 00:08:31.840
for later—which

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:34.350
I have

00:08:34.350 --> 00:08:34.360
been—like,

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:36.790
'One day, Lord, in

00:08:36.790 --> 00:08:36.800
the

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:38.750
sweet by-and-by Megan's going to get

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:41.310
over that.'Why not

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:44.870
now? Mark 11:24: 'Whatsoever things

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:46.230
you desire, when you pray, believe that

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:48.670
you receive them, and you shall have

00:08:48.670 --> 00:08:48.680
them.'Do

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:51.269
you understand? 'Whatever

00:08:51.279 --> 00:08:53.150
things you desire, when you

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:55.670
pray, believe that you receive them, and

00:08:55.680 --> 00:08:57.509
you'll have them.'That's the first part

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:00.470
of the verse.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:02.230
I said,

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:04.389
'Forgive me, Lord,'because

00:09:04.389 --> 00:09:04.399
we

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:07.990
always try to be

00:09:07.990 --> 00:09:08.000
so

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:11.430
spiritual; we try to act like

00:09:11.430 --> 00:09:11.440
we're

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:13.710
faking it, saying 'I'm

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:13.720
believing,'but

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:16.630
are you truly believing?

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:18.190
Are you really believing? That's what He

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.710
was showing me: 'Do you really believe

00:09:19.710 --> 00:09:19.720
this?'I'm

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:21.910
going to question you: do you

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:24.069
really believe your unsaved loved ones

00:09:24.069 --> 00:09:24.079
are

00:09:24.079 --> 00:09:28.550
coming? How would we act if today they

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:31.269
called you and said, 'Mom, Dad, Grandma,

00:09:31.279 --> 00:09:33.389
Grandpa, I got born again

00:09:33.399 --> 00:09:36.110
today'? Instead of 'one day they'll get saved, I'm

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.910
believing before they die they'll get

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:37.920
saved,'what

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:41.949
if we start believing in the

00:09:41.959 --> 00:09:44.269
now? The Lord said, 'Start believing for

00:09:44.279 --> 00:09:44.949
the

00:09:44.949 --> 00:09:44.959
now.'All

00:09:44.959 --> 00:09:47.670
we see about the great

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:47.680
shaking—I'll

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:50.550
go back to

00:09:50.550 --> 00:09:50.560
that—I

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:53.069
know what the Lord has shown me:

00:09:53.079 --> 00:09:55.590
there's a great shaking to awaken. I know there

00:09:55.590 --> 00:09:55.600
are

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:57.670
major things about to take place.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:00.190
It's all about the people

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:03.190
that are coming and running with

00:10:03.190 --> 00:10:03.200
the—we're

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:05.509
ready with the catcher's mitts, ready

00:10:05.519 --> 00:10:07.750
to get the people that are coming.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:10.750
The shaking to awaken is for the great

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:13.190
revival, for us to have this major

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:15.829
outpouring of the Spirit like we had at

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:17.550
these services. We're waiting and

00:10:17.560 --> 00:10:19.829
anticipating the manifestations of the

00:10:19.839 --> 00:10:23.630
glory, saying, 'God, let's do it

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:26.550
tonight. God, let's see somebody get

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:27.990
healed tonight.'Where

00:10:27.990 --> 00:10:28.000
is

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.550
the glorious

00:10:30.550 --> 00:10:30.560
outpouring?

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:32.990
Where's it at, Lord? I'm believing

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.350
it's going to happen

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:38.269
tonight. I'm believing my unsaved loved

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:40.710
one's going to get born again today.

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:43.550
Always have an expectation for the

00:10:43.560 --> 00:10:46.389
manifestation of what you're believing

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:49.910
for, never losing sight of being fully

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:52.030
persuaded that what God has promised,

00:10:52.040 --> 00:10:56.150
He's able also to perform. I believe I

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:58.030
receive what the Lord has told me He

00:10:58.040 --> 00:11:00.910
would do, and I'm not going to get weary

00:11:00.910 --> 00:11:00.920
in

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:02.150
well-doing.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:06.030
I'm going to keep my eyes focused on Him,

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:09.110
seeking Him, staying vertical regardless

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:11.509
of what the finances say, regardless of

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:13.710
what my checkbook says,

00:11:13.710 --> 00:11:13.720
or

00:11:13.720 --> 00:11:16.389
what my bank statement says. I

00:11:16.389 --> 00:11:16.399
am

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:19.910
not moved by what I

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:23.310
see; I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm

00:11:23.310 --> 00:11:23.320
moved

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:25.110
by what the word of God

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:26.389
says. That's what I'm trying to tell you

00:11:26.399 --> 00:11:29.350
all. Many of you are

